{"tid":1774373,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【主流桌面級 Ryzen 16 核未到頂!!】 AMD：只要有軟件配合，核心數會繼續增加","createTime":"2019-12-08T08:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T04:39:37.000Z","uid":28114,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2ca8fcf8b9d047bc3a1870e3344026ebbf80e0","tid":1774373,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T08:27:07.000Z","msg":"從 2017 年帶著 Zen 架構處理器重返高性能 CPU 市場以來，AMD 的 X86 市佔不斷提升，前兩代的 14nm、12nm 處理器才是熱身，今年推出的 7nm Ryzen 及 EPYC 才是主角，伺服器已經達到 64 核心，桌面 HEDT 發燒級頂級型號 Threadripper 3990X 將會成為全世界第一款桌面級 64 核心 128 線程處理器，而主流市場上甚至都到了 16 核心，不過 AMD 並不會停下腳步，在未來將會繼續在&ldquo;核心戰&rdquo;繼續發展。<br />\n<br />\n在伺服器市場上，AMD 的&ldquo;核彈&rdquo;就更狠了，今年 7nm Zen2 架構的 Rome 處理器達到 64 核心、128 線程，而 Intel 的 Xeon 伺服器 CPU 最多依然是 28 核心、56 線程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/11/source/25202344241425358135.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F11%2Fsource%2F25202344241425358135.jpg&h=7e21a603&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n桌面市場上也同樣再次翻倍，16 核 32 線程的 Ryzen 9 3950X 取代以往的 8 核心進入主流市場，而桌面 HEDT 發燒級平台已經有 24 核心、32 核的 Ryzen Threadripper 3960X、3970X，但是 64 核心、128 線程的 RyzenThreadripper 3990X 已經不是秘密了，就是等著明年發布而已。<br />\n <br />\n再往後呢？桌面達到 64 核心之後還會不會再翻倍到 128 線程？AMD CTO Mark Papermaster 在接受採訪時表示，在他看來，主流市場上對於處理器的核心數目並「未到頂」，16 核心當然不會是「終點」，因為軟件正在快速跟上，可以越來越多地充分利用多核心、多線程優勢，因此在短期內，AMD 不會滿足，將會向著更多的核心方向發展。"},{"pid":"38818e72ef76f8fd74b360ce6615431a135b7393","tid":1774373,"uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/12/source/0719011777553003053.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F12%2Fsource%2F0719011777553003053.jpg&h=be51530d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMark Papermaster 也承認，增加核心數必須小心，避免浪費，必須做好軟件配合，這是一個平衡，會繼續下去。Papermaster 表示，Infinity Fabric 高速互連總線會持續演進，滿足更高頻寬技術標準的需求，例如 DDR5、PCIe 5.0。<br />\n <br />\n從目前的趨勢看，AMD 有望在 2021-2022 年間上馬 DDR5、PCIe 5.0。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/09/source/11193243632038138220.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F09%2Fsource%2F11193243632038138220.jpg&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7EkcxSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=16052885\" target=\"_blank\">https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/09/source/11193243632038138220.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/18757/主流桌面級_Ryzen_16_核未到頂_AMD只要有軟件配合核心數會繼續增加\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F18757%2F%E4%B8%BB%E6%B5%81%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%B4%9A_Ryzen_16_%E6%A0%B8%E6%9C%AA%E5%88%B0%E9%A0%82_AMD%E5%8F%AA%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E8%BB%9F%E4%BB%B6%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%83%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7EkcxSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=3525b801\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkepc.com/18757/主流桌面級_Ryzen_16_核未到頂_AMD只要有軟件配合核心數會繼續增加</a>"},{"pid":"e7669fa468ba5baa7dd13551ef3b252df9259627","tid":1774373,"uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"AMD Yes"},{"pid":"1200c21d20db9ec2526d681acc9e7016c902a892","tid":1774373,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":51,"score":-49,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T09:50:45.000Z","msg":"咁撚多CORE有乜用<br />\n提升單春性能好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214c00c0f175b0f8aeda746bd3ec933150698b75","tid":1774373,"uid":77192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1200c21d20db9ec2526d681acc9e7016c902a892","tid":1774373,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":51,"score":-49,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T09:50:45.000Z","msg":"咁撚多CORE有乜用<br />\n提升單春性能好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T09:53:17.000Z","msg":"物理問題製程越細，單核性能越難提升"},{"pid":"407c6b9513230ce94e568297c7e75f53255128e5","tid":1774373,"uid":112760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1200c21d20db9ec2526d681acc9e7016c902a892","ti